originalText.text:
I was originally referred to Dr. Rafii by a nurse with VNSNY. My mother was looking for a new Primary Care doctor & the nurse had told me he had heard wonderful feedback from his patients about Dr. Rafii.

The office is always helpful in scheduling appointments for my mother as soon as possible.

I found the care for my mother from Dr. Rafii to be excellent and we continue to see him for her needs on an ongoing basis.

I am happy to recommend Dr. Rafii to anyone (especially a senior) looking for a new doctor.

originalText.text: I found Dr. Rafii to be wonderful! I am 78 with multiple health issues and he was both caring and thorough in providing care to me. When he needed to refer me to other providers, they were also all excellent.

originalText.text: I've been Dr Rafiis, patient for a long time. This doctor & his staff are #1 In my book. They don't make doctors like this no more. I pray he never retires. You won't be disappointed.
